# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in the values you have.
# Every variable is OPTIONAL — the site will run without them,
# but live follower counts will fall back to scraping, then to
# the hardcoded values in src/app/api/followers/route.ts.

# ---------- Instagram Graph API ----------
# Required together. Without these, Instagram count falls back to scraping.
#   1. Connect an Instagram Business or Creator account to a Facebook Page
#   2. Create a Facebook App at https://developers.facebook.com
#   3. Add the "Instagram Graph API" product
#   4. Generate a long-lived access token (60 days; refreshable)
#   5. Fetch your IG user ID via the Graph API Explorer
IG_USER_ID=
IG_ACCESS_TOKEN=

# ---------- TikTok Display API v2 ----------
# Without this, TikTok count falls back to scraping.
#   1. Register as a developer at https://developers.tiktok.com
#   2. Create an app, add the "Display API" product
#   3. OAuth flow with the account owner to obtain an access token
#   4. Note: tokens expire — plan for refresh logic
TIKTOK_ACCESS_TOKEN=

# ---------- Airtable (currently unused) ----------
# The contact buttons link to public Airtable forms directly (no key needed).
# Kept here in case server-side Airtable integration is added later
# (e.g. fetching client logos, reading form submissions, etc.).
AIRTABLE_API_KEY=
